"This is a common-sense bill to bolster Department of Homeland Security programs and policies to enhance the DHS relationship with State and local fusion centers across the country." #HR5079

"I recently visited the Nebraska Information Analysis Center (NIAC) and saw firsthand the hard work and commitment from these partners to help protect our nation from another terrorist attack."
